"""
proton-drive-setup — Proton Drive credential wizard (A2 milestone).

GTK dialog that authenticates via proton-drive-helper (SRP), handles
CAPTCHA challenges via direct API calls (image puzzle), then stores the
session tokens in the GNOME keyring.  The password is never written to disk.

Requirements: python3-gi  gir1.2-gtk-4.0 (or gir1.2-gtk-3.0)
              proton-drive-helper  secret-tool
"""

